DOC_LEVEL: L2
MODULE: runtime/services
PATH: src/services/**
DESCRIPTION: runtime service layer for chat/session/system actions plus pipeline control facade

KEY_FILES:
- src/services/chat-service.js
- src/services/chat-queue.js
- src/services/session-store.js
- src/services/realtime-hub.js
- src/services/system-exec-service.js
- src/services/pipeline-control-service.js
- src/services/pipeline-controller.js
- src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js
- src/services/status-aggregator.js
- src/services/log-pager.js
- src/services/telegram-pusher.js
- src/services/git-service.js
- src/services/commit-service.js
- src/services/command-executor-service.js
- src/services/output-pager-service.js
- src/services/file-service.js
- src/services/system-monitor-service.js
- src/services/alert-manager-service.js

PUBLIC_APIS:
- chatWithSession({ channel, sessionId, message, realtimeHooks })
- resetSession({ channel, sessionId })
- pipeline control: startPipeline/getPipelineStatus/stopPipeline/retryTarget/getPipelineLogs/resetTarget
- pipeline controller (F-004): createPipelineController -> startPipeline/stopPipeline/retryTarget/runSingle/getStatus/getLogs/forceUnlock
- plan ingestion: validate/save/listVersions/getVersion/setCurrent/getCurrent/rollback/getActivePath
- status aggregator (F-005): createStatusAggregator -> aggregateStatus/formatStatusForTelegram/calculateProgress/getErrorSummary
- log pager (F-005): createLogPager -> readLogPage/extractErrorLines/shouldSendAsFile/formatLogsForTelegram
- telegram pusher (F-005): createTelegramPusher -> startHeartbeat/stopHeartbeat/pushErrorSummary/sendMessageChunked/sendFile
- git service (F-008): createGitService -> getStatus/isClean/getChangedFiles/commit/amendCommit/getLastCommit/getCommitLog/getShortHash
- commit service (F-008): createCommitService -> validatePreConditions/commit/recordCommit/getSessionCommits/checkPipelineStatus/checkTestStatus/buildCommitMessage
- command executor (F-009): executeCommand/confirmHighRiskCommand -> blacklist check, high-risk detection, confirmation flow, cwd support, output pagination
- output pager (F-009): paginateOutput/storeOutputPages/getNextPage/clearPages/hasMorePages -> Telegram 4096 char limit handling
- file service (F-010): validatePath/resolveSessionPath/listDirectory/buildTree/readFile/searchFiles/writeFile/isBinaryFile -> file operations with path validation
- system monitor (F-012): getSystemInfo/getProcessList/killProcess/formatUptime/formatBytes -> CPU/memory/disk/network info, process management
- alert manager (F-012): addRule/removeRule/listRules/checkThresholds/startMonitoring/stopMonitoring/loadRules/saveRules/parseRuleString -> threshold alerting with persistence

TRAPS:
- chat operations are serialized by session key; keep async queue semantics unchanged
- pipeline-control-service must delegate to script-runner instead of shell string concatenation
- pipeline-controller must use lock-manager for concurrency protection (F-004)
- runSingle must NOT acquire lock (independent execution, D5)
- file-service validatePath checks against config.telegramFileAllowedRoots (frozen at startup)
- file-service resolves symlinks and re-validates against allowed roots for security

DECISIONS:
- 2026-03-10 | f001-pipeline-service | expose logs/reset methods in pipeline-control-service to satisfy US3 reusable control surface
- 2026-03-12 | f003-plan-ingestion | add plan-ingestion-service for schema validation, version management, and plan registry
- 2026-03-12 | f004-pipeline-controller | new module for unified pipeline control with lock management (D4)
- 2026-03-13 | f005-status-logs | add status-aggregator, log-pager, telegram-pusher for pipeline status aggregation and log streaming
- 2026-03-15 | f008-commit-workflow | add git-service and commit-service for commit workflow with pre-commit validation, audit logging (AC-5.3)
- 2026-03-15 | f008-exception-handling | add try-catch blocks in commit() function around validatePreConditions, gitService.commit/amendCommit, recordCommit, logAuditEntry calls to prevent crashes and ensure errors logged to audit trail
- 2026-03-16 | f009-command-executor | add command-executor-service and output-pager-service for general shell command execution with blacklist, high-risk keywords, confirmation flow, session cwd, and pagination
- 2026-03-13 | f010-file-service | add file-service for directory listing, tree building, file reading/writing, and glob search with path validation
- 2026-03-13 | f012-system-monitor | add system-monitor-service and alert-manager-service for system info, process management, and threshold-based alerting with persistence
